* Iterative Processing\nwith For Each
** Purpose
***_ Apply same logic across multiple items
***_ Eliminates repetitive task definitions
***_ Single nested task definition
** Input Sources
***_ Defined directly as JSON
***_ From preceding task value
***_ From a job parameter
** Common Scenarios
***_ Process files from path list
***_ Transform per region/date range
***_ Analysis across product categories
** Concurrency
***_ Control parallel iterations
***_ Higher = faster, more compute
@endmindmap
